# T-Mobile 核心网 IP 段
IP-CIDR,208.54.0.0/16,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.94.0.0/19,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,206.29.177.36/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,172.56.0.0/12,no-resolve
